dct_title_s: Mapa geográfico de la Republica Argentina
dct_alternative_sm: Argentine Republic as a field for European emigration a statistical and geographical review of the country and its resources with all its various features
dct_description_sm: grabado por Curt Stiller ; litografia de Alberto Larsch.
From The Argentine Republic as a field for European emigration / F. Latzina. Buenos Aires : Printing establishment "The Union," of Stiller & Laass, 1883.
Insets: Plano topográfico de las colónias agrícolas de Santa-Fé -- Situacion de la República Argentina en la América del Sud -- Plano de la ciudad de Buenos Aires capital de la República Argentina.
Accompanying text on verso in English.
Available also through the Norman B. Leventhal Map Center website as a raster image.
